pyc4
-------------------------------------------
Py Connect Four is a simple connect four game.  The classic!  
This is a 2 player game where each player enters their name, then take 
turns putting their pieces in trying to get 4 in a row first.

Runtime requirements:
  python-2.5.1-1
  python-pygame-1.7.1-2

Canonical homepage:
  http://members.fortunecity.com/6ft_dan/Connect_Four/

Canonical download:
  http://downloads.sourceforge.net/pyc4/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack pyc4-1.7b-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./pyc4-1.7b-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pyc4-1.7b-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/pyc4-1.7b-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

